{"tid":2136272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華大疑招聘內地護士來港","createTime":"2020-08-02T04:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T12:12:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"073b04bfddc4f2d6bd20e9d93b367a2aaed910a8","tid":2136272,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T04:45:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/OHLNKE2WNOX2JAXFQFFXAJVBN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FOHLNKE2WNOX2JAXFQFFXAJVBN4%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=812a5338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FOHLNKE2WNOX2JAXFQFFXAJVBN4%2F&h=57b617d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/OHLNKE2WNOX2JAXFQFFXAJVBN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華大疑招聘內地護士來港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tNNnMKbBkHfdbl6TRRolofS4lyU=/438x560/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P5FFZUQE5UW3UV2PEI72GPMAMU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtNNnMKbBkHfdbl6TRRolofS4lyU%3D%2F438x560%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP5FFZUQE5UW3UV2PEI72GPMAMU.gif&h=37349b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府早前將高危人士病毒檢測工作外判予三間公司，包括來自內地的華大基因旗下華昇診斷中心。有內地微博賬戶發佈一張聲稱是華大基因的招聘廣告（圖），招聘咽拭子採集員，需有護士資格、港澳通行證及在港工作，綜合薪金達三萬港元。醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明表示，目前公立醫院是由護士為病人抽取鼻咽樣本，若該廣告屬實，擔心有人以抽取樣本非護理工作為由，繞過正常程序安排內地護士來港工作。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：亞博啟用收30患者 走廊漏水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工會憂走法律罅<br />\n<br />\n翻查華大基因官方網頁，未見有相關招聘廣告，也未知招聘是否與內地協助本港進行大規模檢測有關。政府早前將為約40萬名高危人士做病毒檢測的工作，沒招標下交予三間私營化驗所，包括華大基因旗下的華昇診斷中心。華昇以採集咽拭子樣本的方法進行病毒檢測。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港《護士註冊條例 》，無執業證明書的人不得執業為註冊護士 ，但若在解放軍中服務或由政府全職僱用，則可豁免註冊。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，繞過正常程序安排內地護士來港，「擺明無牌做嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n衞生服務界立法。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。交代有關人員來港，是否同需遵守隔離14日的規定。有關人員的工作範圍是否涉及政府檢測項目，其薪金是否政府支付。"},{"pid":"0ca44d7ff0365188f2204c34a3ba4cdf0fc97cce","tid":2136272,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"Push sin"},{"pid":"a29f568bd71dd09f5d903991a6158deebe26a44e","tid":2136272,"uid":27482,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"政府比錢即係我交稅又係俾埋班廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c3383d8be98ab6b9da29c29d99b65314ee2927","tid":2136272,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a8239f706356382cd35506c1dd77f6e20a7d6a","tid":2136272,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"點解要40歲或以下？"},{"pid":"6067b807222c9dff51aed9efdf87efa9d8d52de6","tid":2136272,"uid":48767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"快啦，終於人手可以追國際比例了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746e67983474b6cf4a421f1413300659b9348482","tid":2136272,"uid":36134,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:03:49.000Z","msg":"個人工擺明係港共出錢啦...."},{"pid":"16ce54a2bac791d4bbd8549d1242e079e64d66b8","tid":2136272,"uid":312033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1a8239f706356382cd35506c1dd77f6e20a7d6a","tid":2136272,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"點解要40歲或以下？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"夜晚仲有第二份工"},{"pid":"7df0431e53a1ada9246b64bd52c97152e6c4b84c","tid":2136272,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f547a1dad47d881eea8a33df9ebf559017a423","tid":2136272,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":